===Etymology===
Arabic "lapis lazuli". see also French ''[[azur]]'' and Italian ''[[azzurro]]''

===Noun===
#A [[blue]] colour, represented in engraving by horizontal parallel lines.
#The clear blue colour of the sky; also, a pigment or dye of this colour.
